@{u}@{b}Iconify@{ub}@{uu}
  This menu item shrinks The Tag Thing's window to the height of just the title
bar.  In this iconified state The Tag Thing has a Project menu with three
items:  @{b}UnIconify@{ub}, @{b}About@{ub}, and @{b}Quit@{ub}.

  The window's zoom gadget may be used to uniconify the window.

 ________________________________
|o|  The Tag Thing  v0.6  |' ||[]|       @{bg shine}@{u}Project        @{uu}@{bg background}
 --------------------------------        @{bg shine}Uniconify  [A]I@{bg background}
