@node WANTED "The Tag Thing:  Now It's Your Turn!"

Plug-Ins
  If you write a plug-in script, or improve one of the current ones, send it to
me and I'll include it with future releases and on the Web page.


Interesting Uses
  So far, uses for The Tag Thing include inserting taglines, AmigaGuide tags,
and HTML tags.  So what are @{u}you@{uu} using it for?  If you've found a different/
unique use for The Tag Thing I'd like to hear about it.


  Be creative (but then you're an Amiga user; what else would you be?)!

  Click @{"here" link SMEGHEAD} for information on how to contact me.
@endnode


@node WASDONE "The Tag Thing:  Binary Archaeology"

@{u}@{b}History:@{ub}@{uu}
  A long time ago, on a hard drive far, far away...

@{b}0.7:@{ub}
  - The search pattern is now "#?<Find gadget's contents>#?".
    - Suggested by Jonh Pullicino
  - Find direction menu items and startup option to set the initial search
   direction.
  - A search may automatically be performed once a pattern is entered into the
   Find gadget.
    - Suggested by Jonh Pullicino
  - The iconified window is now named "TheTagThing"; makes it a little
   thinner.
  - Undo, Redo, and Flush now work.  Adding, deleting, or editing quotes may
   be undone/redone.
  - New startup option:  MAXUNDO.
  - Updated the interface-update routine.
  - The About requester now displays the number of items in the undo buffer.

@{b}0.6b:@{ub}
  - Fixed some string-related bugs.

@{b}0.6a:@{ub}
  - Some optimising in the argument parsing routine.
  - Disabled the Undo menus and gadgets.
  - Fixed a small bug in the file requester routine.

@{b}0.6:@{ub}
  - New start-up option:  DEFAULTDRAWER, based on a suggestion by Gerald
   Schnabel.
  - Eliminated an inefficient bit of code.
  - Improved the "Quit:  Are you sure?" requester that pops up when the tags
   have been modified.
  - An updated TagToCED.rexx, by Gerald Schnabel.
  - Included TagToEd.rexx, another plug-in by Gerald Schnabel.

@{b}0.5:@{ub}
  - Save will open a file requester if the Tag File gadget is blank.
  - Create Icons no longer overwrites existing icons.
  - A new plug-in, TagToCED.rexx, has been recieved and included.  Thanks to
   Gerald Schnabel for this.
  - An updated HTMLTags.txt, by Gregory Donner.
  - Somehow forgot to include the TagToEdge.rexx plug-in in the last release.
   Oops.


@{b}0.4:@{ub}
  - Initial public release.
  - All features except for Undo/Redo working.  Only a couple of minor bugs.
@endnode


